::Hot Rod/Prowl/Epyon/Skyburst::

He closed the link.
"Sounds like they are being faced with a lot of enemies. Good thing we
are bringing a big force. We cant wait any longer. C'mon!"
Hot Rod transforms to car mode and heads out.

"Alright, lets go all. Beast mode!"
Prowl transformes to his owl/raptor mode, and takes off after Hot Rod.

"Epyon, dragon mode!"
Epyon transformes to his transmetal dragon mode, and also takes off.

"I'm ready to kick some ass!"
Skyburst transformes to his army helicoptor mode, following the others.

Khonkolor, Goth, Ghost, and the Xenoforce would have to leave quickly to
keep up.
